<note n="270-2">This is engraved in continuation of No. 61 above.</note>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu <unclear>yādava</unclear>nārāyaṇaṁ
<lb n="2"/>nissaṁka pratāpacakravartti hoysaṇa
<lb n="3"/>śrīvīraballāḷadēva varṣada <unclear>22</unclear> neya Āṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>girasa saṁvatsarada <unclear>vaiśākha</unclear> suddha 13 Ā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>divāradaṁdu śrīmallokkiguṁḍiyūroḍeya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pramukhavaśēṣa mahājanaṁ śrīsāsirvvara sa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁnidhānadalu śrīmadhusūdanadēvargge
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> seṭṭiyaru nityārādhaneya
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> biṭṭa gadyāṇa 5 paṇa <unclear>1</unclear> yī
<lb n="10"/>hoṁna vriddhiyalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yara sō
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mayyanuṁ nāyaka <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> sōmayya
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nuṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> pratipā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ḷisuvaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> maṁgaḷa mahā śrī śrī
</p>

